column5: Afternoon All,  Hope everyone’s Easter went well…  I got out on Sunday morning for some weekend steel. Here are some pictures I went 5/6… The day started out bad when we slept in, but it turned out to be a great day out.  Enjoy…        Days like these make me wanna ditch work and hit the rivers…  Joe
Looks like it was a pretty grey day  , Nice fish.
nice fish have fun. I guess that is the french river.
nice fish to bad u ruined the photo
Hey man, those are some nice fish WTG!
Love the big buck in the last pic. RF
nice ones,congrats on a good day
Nice work Dobee,..great shots,...Huge buck in the last pic,...cheers!!

I personally want to know what happened to the rest of his hat?...  G

LOL   Nice fish though, good job.
